clientSide.Stubs

Class ArrivalTerminalTransferQuayStub

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientSide.Stubs.ArrivalTerminalTransferQuayStub

  • public class ArrivalTerminalTransferQuayStub
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the Arrival Terminal Transfer Quay Stub. This file consists on the implementation of the Arrival Terminal Transfer Quay's shared region functions, but in a message approach version. In each function, a connection is established and a message is sent to the Arrival Terminal Transfer Quay Interface that will execute the proper function from the original shared region itself.
